{{Quote|I wonder if we can find a vet droid in Anchorhead?|[[Biggs Darklighter/Legends|Biggs Darklighter]] to [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] concerning a dying [[Bantha/Legends|bantha]]|<ref name="The Essential Guide to Alien Species (real-world book)">[[The Essential Guide to Alien Species (real-world book)|''The Essential Guide to Alien Species'']]</ref>}}
'''Vet droid''' was the name given to any [[Medical droid/Legends|medical droid]] designed for or specializing in treatment of animals. They were known to be active as of the time of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], though it was apparently hard to find vet droids in small townships such as [[Anchorhead/Legends|Anchorhead]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]].

